back to the States.

38
00:05:22,160 --> 00:05:24,704
I explained the law in detail myself.

39
00:05:24,829 --> 00:05:27,542
But there’s no law
which says he can’t marry her,

40
00:05:27,667 --> 00:05:30,503
and he’s appealed to his congressman.

41
00:05:30,628 --> 00:05:34,215
- His congressman?
- I wish you’d talk to him.

42
00:05:34,340 --> 00:05:38,511
