and busted right back again.

45
00:05:49,815 --> 00:05:52,943
Yeah, my congressman.
Shocking, ain’t it, Major?

46
00:05:53,068 --> 00:05:56,530
Chaplain says don’t marry the girl.
Colonel says don’t marry the girl.

47
00:05:56,655 --> 00:05:58,700
