that girl, Kelly.” What can I do?

49
00:06:03,329 --> 00:06:07,125
I’ll tell you what you can do, boy.
You can go and marry your congressman.

50
00:06:07,250 --> 00:06:09,294
You’d be better off.

51
00:06:10,128 --> 00:06:12,547
Give me coffee.

52
00:06:12,672 --> 00:06:14,717
Yes, sir.

53
00:06:16,760 --> 00:06:20,472
I hear you bagged two more today, Major.

54
00:06:20,598 --> 00:06:23,475
- How was it up there?
- Splendid.

55
00:06:27,229 --> 00:06:30,775
