that we oughta talk about.

74
00:07:43,853 --> 00:07:47,106
- What do you mean?
- Well, now listen.

75
00:07:47,232 --> 00:07:50,318
I never did show you
a picture of my girl, did I, Kelly?

76
00:07:50,443 --> 00:07:51,820
No.

77
00:07:51,945 --> 00:07:55,365
Well, I’m gonna show you
a picture of a girl.

78
00:07:55,490 --> 00:07:58,076
