115
00:10:14,722 --> 00:10:17,850
- Will they, Kelly?
- I ain’t got any family.

116
00:10:17,975 --> 00:10:21,478
I haven’t got anything
against this girl of yours.

117
00:10:21,604 --> 00:10:26,109
