153
00:13:01,191 --> 00:13:05,695
See that little park over there with
the lakes around it? That’s Matsubayashi.

154
00:13:05,820 --> 00:13:08,448
- Where?
- Right down in there. See it?

155
00:13:08,573 --> 00:13:11,493
