are the most famous in Japan.

156
00:13:11,618 --> 00:13:14,704
They sing, they dance,
they act all the parts. No men.

157
00:13:14,829 --> 00:13:17,875
Katsumi knows all the actresses.
She’s a movie fan.

158
00:13:18,000 --> 00:13:23,256
You’re just blowin’ your top about
seeing Katsumi, aren’t you? Carryin’ on...

159
00:13:23,381 --> 00:13:25,424
She’s my girl, Major.

160
00:13:39,731 --> 00:13:42,359
- Well, GG, good to see you.
- So long, Lloyd.

161
00:13:42,484 --> 00:13:46,071
- Lots of luck to you.
- Thank you. Bye-bye.

162
00:13:47,114 --> 00:13:49,450
Lloyd! Lloyd! Here we are.

163
00:13:49,576 --> 00:13:51,244
Lloyd!

164
00:13:51,369 --> 00:13:54,247
