but who is that good-looking woman?”

178
00:14:54,978 --> 00:14:59,900
- Tell me about Eileen. How is she?
- She finds Tulsa terribly dull without you.

179
00:15:00,025 --> 00:15:02,861
Well, I wish she could have come along.

180
00:15:02,986 --> 00:15:06,281
Lloyd, you couldn’t expect us
to bring her out here.

181
00:15:06,406 --> 00:15:10,370
You’re registered at the hotel for the first
few nights but stationed here after that.

182
00:15:10,495 --> 00:15:13,081
- I see.
- Let’s go. You get in first.

183
00:15:13,206 --> 00:15:16,626
- You go ahead, Mrs. Webster.
- No, you get in first.

184
00:15:16,751 --> 00:15:19,379
- Go on, get in.
- No, ladies first.

185
00:15:22,633 --> 00:15:23,884
Hi, Lloyd.

186
00:15:25,344 --> 00:15:27,513
You devil.

187
00:15:27,638 --> 00:15:29,682
Come here.

188
