199
00:16:30,663 --> 00:16:33,833
Please, Mike, let’s go.

200
00:16:35,251 --> 00:16:37,462
- What’s she doing here?
- Mother!

201
00:16:37,587 --> 00:16:42,801
- Isn’t she with that young officer?
- Kobe’s a recreation centre.

202
00:16:42,927 --> 00:16:45,262
- That’s right.
- It degrades the uniform.

203
00:16:45,387 --> 00:16:48,390
- It’s out-and-out fraternization.
- She’s beautiful.

204
00:16:48,515 --> 00:16:49,975
All the more reason.

205
00:16:50,100 --> 00:16:52,144
Mark?

206
00:16:52,269 --> 00:16:53,896
Colonel Crawford.

207
00:16:54,021 --> 00:16:58,652
- Let’s get outta this clip joint.
- Just a minute, Captain Bailey.

208
00:16:58,777 --> 00:17:03,156
- What’s the trouble?
- I didn’t mean to bother you with this.

209
00:17:03,281 --> 00:17:06,409
